    <item>
      <title>苹果因 Spotify 纠纷将面临欧盟近 5 亿欧元罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/apple-set-to-face-near-500-million-eu-fine-in-spotify-row</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司将面临欧盟近 5 亿欧元（5.39 亿美元）的罚款，原因是监管机构正在调查苹果公司在其平台上压制音乐流媒体竞争对手（包括 Spotify Technology SA）的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/apple-set-to-face-near-500-million-eu-fine-in-spotify-row</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 16:36:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
